  "translations": {
    "en": "'Do you know what you did with Yusuf and his brother when you were ignorant?' They said: 'Are you indeed Yusuf?' He said: 'I am Yusuf and this is my brother. Allah has certainly been gracious to us. Indeed, whoever fears Allah and is patient, then indeed Allah does not allow to be lost the reward of those who do good.' They said: 'By Allah, certainly Allah has preferred you over us, and indeed we have been sinners.' He said: 'No blame will there be upon you today. May Allah forgive you, and He is the most merciful of the merciful.'",
